gnify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a rope)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became tightly twisted."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b2-  And hence, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, became strong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"firm, like a rope tightly twisted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the following phrases.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astmr~ biAl$~aYo'i","text_ar":"استمرّ بِالشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became strong to bear the thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K. [See an ex. in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSomaEu","text_ar":"اَصْمَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astmr~ mariyruhu","text_ar":"استمرّ مَرِيرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became firm;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astmr~t mariyratuhu","text_ar":"استمرّت مَرِيرَتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his resolution,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"determination, became firm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became strong, after being weak:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astmr~t mariyratuhu","text_ar":"استمرّت مَرِيرَتُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his resistance"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$akiymap","text_ar":"شَكِيمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became firm."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astmr~t mariyratuhu Ealayohi","text_ar":"استمرّت مَرِيرَتُهُ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became firm against him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his resistance"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$akiymap","text_ar":"شَكِيمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, became strong:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became accustomed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"habituated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inured,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a tropical signification, from the twisting of a rope. (TA.) ―         -b3-  [And hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astmr~","text_ar":"استمرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state of affairs, became right, after having been bad"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corrupt:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh, T, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he repented, and became good, righteous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"virtuous."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A [but not given as tropical].)       -A3-  As syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amar~a","text_ar":"اَمَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mar~a","text_ar":"مَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of food, &c.: see 4."}],"source_refs":["M","K","Mgh","Msb","A","S","TA","ISh","T"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}